  48: expected_tier_distribution:
  49:   - tier: T1
  50:     min_fraction: 0.30
  51:     max_fraction: 0.60
  52:     rationale: >
  53:       Peer-reviewed primary studies (RCTs, cohort, case-control) are the
  54:       foundation of clinical efficacy and safety claims.
  55:   - tier: T2
  56:     min_fraction: 0.15
  57:     max_fraction: 0.40
  58:     rationale: >
  59:       Systematic reviews and meta-analyses consolidate primary evidence
